quran[14]{c,v,t}:
  28,29,"Ke kaloku ukuligqiba kwakhe uMûsâ ixesha wahamba nosapho lwakhe, wabona umlilo ngasentabeni yeTûr. Wathi kusapho lwakhe: “Hlalani apha; inene mna ndibone umlilo. Mhlawumbi ndiya kuniphathela kuwo apho inkcazelo ethile okanye isikhuni esivuthayo ukuze nizifudumeze ngaso.”"
  28,30,"Kodwa wathi akusondela kuwo, wabizwa ngakwicala lasekunene lentili kwindawo esikelelekileyo emthini (kwathiwa kuye): “Wena Mûsâ, inene Mna NdinguAllah, iNkosi yamaphakade.”"
  28,31,"“Jula phantsi umsimelelo wakho.” Kodwa wathi akuwubona ubhinyalaza okwenyoka, wajika wabaleka, akanyeka nokunyeka. UAllâh Wathi: Hini na Mûsâ sondela ungoyiki. Inene wena ungomnye wabakhuselekileyo"
  28,32,"Faka isandla sakho ekuvulekeni kwesambatho sakho; siya kuphuma simhlophe, singenasifo. Uze uphinde usondeze ingalo yakho kuwe (ukuthintela) uloyiko, kuba leyo yimiqondiso emibini evela eNkosini yakho isiya kuFir’awn neenkosi zakhe. Inene bona ngabantu abangabenzi bobubi.”"
  28,33,"Wathi yena: “Nkosi yam, inene mna ndabulala umntu phakathi kwabo, yaye ndinoloyiko lokuba baya kundibulala (nam)"
  28,34,"Ukanti umntakwethu uHârûn nguyena uliciko kunam ngokolwimi, ngoko ke mthume kunye nam njengomncedisi, ukuze andingqinele. Inene mna ndoyika ukuba baza kundiphika.”"
  28,35,"UAllâhWathi:“Siyakuyomelezaingaloyakhongomntakwenu Size Sininike nobabini ubukhulu ukuze bangafikeleli kuni. (Kuya kwenzeka oko) ngemiqondiso yeThu; Nina nobabini nabo balandela nina niya kuba nokongamela.”"
  28,36,"Kodwa wathi uMûsâ esakufika kubo nemiqondiso yeThu ibubungqina obucacileyo, bathi bona: “Oku akunto yimbi ngaphandle kwemilingo eqanjiweyo, yaye asizanga siyive le (nkolo) koobawo mkhulu bethu.”"
  28,37,"UMûsâ wathi: “INkosi yam yiYo Eyaziyo (kunathi nani) ukuba ngubani na oze nesiKhokelo esivela kuYo"
  28,38,"UFir’awn wathi: Hini na nina zinkosi, andinazi ninathixo wumbi ngaphandle kwam. Ngoko ke wena Hâmân ndiphembele (umlilo unditshisele izitena) zodongwe, undakhele ibhotwe eliphakamileyo3 ukuze ndinyuke ngalo ndiye kuThixo kaMûsâ. Kodwa mna ngokokubona kwam ndicinga ukuba uMûsâ ngomnye wakumaxoki"
  28,39,"Kananjalo yena (uFir’awn) namajoni akhe babekhukhumele elizweni, ngokungekho lungelweni, yaye babecinga ukuba abayi kubuyela kuThi"
  28,40,"Samhlasela ke kunye nemikhosi yakhe, Saza Sabaphosa bonke elwandle. Khangela ke okokuba saba njani na isiphelo sabenzi bobubi"
  28,41,"Yaye Sabenza iinkokeli ezimemela (abantu) (eMlilweni: ukanti ngeMini yokuGqibela, abayi kuncedwa)"
  28,42,"Kananjalo Senza isiqalekiso ukuba sibalandele kweli hlabathi, kanti ngoMhla woVuko baya kuba ngabanye babo banyelekileyo"